clues.clue_text:
Behind silent shutters where no voices stay; 
 A hidden pulse keeps night from swallowing day; 
 Still as stone; but never dead
 Where does the campus draw its thread?

Rang asmaan ke jameen se jude; 
Leharon ka gyan pr khudh stir khade....
Jaha rukna hi behna hai or behna hi kho jana .
